🎥 **1. “AI vs Human Coders — Kaun Jeetega Future Mein?” 🤖👨‍💻

Category: Tech Opinion | AI Future

🎧 Script (Hindi-English Mix, Humanized)

> “AI ab har jagah hai — code likh raha hai, bugs fix kar raha hai, even poore projects bana raha hai 😳

Par ek sawaal sabke dimaag mein hai — kya AI human coders ko replace kar dega?

Mera answer simple hai — Nahi!
AI ek tool hai, coder ke dimaag ka replacement nahi 🧠

Jo coder AI ke saath kaam karna seekh gaya — wahi future mein jeetega 💪

Tum batao — AI threat hai ya opportunity? Comment karo niche 👇”



