Aur mera jawab hamesha same hai — Bilkul ban sakte ho! 😎

Degree ek paper hai, lekin skill ek power hai ⚡

Companies dekhte hain aap kya bana sakte ho, na ki aapke marks.

Agar tum real projects pe kaam karte ho — tumhara career already start ho gaya 💻

