🎥 **3. “Python Developer Kitna Kamaata Hai?” 💰🐍

Category: Career / Real Talk

🎧 Script (Natural Hindi-English)

> “Sabse popular sawaal — Python developer kitna kama leta hai? 💭

Beginner level pe — ₹30,000 se ₹60,000 tak.
Intermediate coders — ₹1 lakh+ per month 💼
Freelancers aur data scientists — ₹2 lakh+ tak easily 😎

Lekin yaad rakho — ye sab depend karta hai tumhare skill aur projects pe.

So focus on learning, not earning — paise khud aa jayenge 💸”



