🎥 **4. “Beginners Coding Kyu Chhod Dete Hain?” 💀💻

Category: Motivation / Real Talk

🎧 Script (Human & Relatable)

> “Yeh ek hard truth hai — 70% beginners coding start karte hain, par 1 mahine mein hi chhod dete hain 😔

Kyun? Kyunki unhe lagta hai coding unke bas ki baat nahi.

Par bhai, har expert coder pehle beginner hi tha 💪

Difference sirf itna hai — wo rukke nahi!

Agar tum daily 1 ghanta bhi practice karte ho, ek saal baad result khud bolega 🔥

So don’t quit, consistency hi sabse bada skill hai!”



