💡 Filming Tips for Humanized Shorts (Face Reveal):

✅ Speak like you’re talking to your friend — not to the camera.
✅ Maintain light smile & direct eye contact.
✅ Add English captions (auto-generated or manual).
✅ Keep background minimal — focus on face + lighting.
✅ Use lo-fi or upbeat background music (not too loud).


